<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
  <html lang="ko">
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body>
  <div class="mt-5"></div>
  <form action="/home_enrollment" method="POST">
    <input type="hidden" name="user_id" value = <%=current_user.id%>>
    <div class="form-group row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-10">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <p>
            <h5><i class="fa fa-user-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> 하숙 등록</h5>
          </p>
          <p>
            <label class="form-control-label" for="house_name">하숙집 이름</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="house_name" name ="house_name" placeholder="">
          </p>
          <p>
            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-group col-md-3">
                <label for="inputEmail4" class="col-form-label">우편번호</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputEmail4" name="post_code" placeholder="'-'를 빼고 입력하세요">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-9">
                <label for="inputPassword4" class="col-form-label">주소</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputPassword4" name="address" placeholder="ex) 서울시 용산구 청파로 47길 100">
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="inputAddress" class="col-form-label">상세주소</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputAddress" name="detail_address" placeholder="ex) 숙명여자대학교">
            </div>
          </p>
          <p>
            <label class="form-control-label" for="user_phone">하숙집 연락처</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="user_phone" name ="phone_number"placeholder="">
          </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="text-primary text-center">* 하숙집은 등록 후 수정 및 삭제가 어렵습니다. *<br> * 신중하게 등록해주세요. *</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class ="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-6" >
        <button class='btn btn-block a_btn_primary mb-5'>등록하기</button>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</body>